item.title: Shaanxi Ghost Train Station, Section 2 (I am a rabbit)
item.description: 7 March 16, 1994 Wang Jun had two homes, one in a building and one in a bungalow with a courtyard. He died in the building, the cause of death was taking a lot of sleeping pills. There is nothing much to say about the death scene, except that there are signs of vomiting, the whole body is quite calm. But in the bungalow, we found a lot of things related to the case.
